➜永州蓝山：八月瓜 采摘忙
http://www.sohu.com/a/423005566_100180399	7137
<p style="text-align: center;"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20201007/823a364d897c48cab7fddac3b040c17c.jpeg" /></p>
